---
/**
 * InfoModal Component
 * Modal containing app information and control references.
 */
---
<div id="info-modal" class="modal-overlay" hidden>
  <div class="modal-box info-box">
    <h3 class="modal-title">
      <svg class="tb-logo-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" width="20" height="20">
        <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.6"></circle>
        <path d="M10 16c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.7 6 6-2.7 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
        <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="2.5" fill="currentColor"></circle>
      </svg>
      STRUDEL-APP INFO
    </h3>
    
    <div class="info-content">
      <p class="lead">Strudel is a live coding environment for creating music using JavaScript.</p>
      <p>It is a web-based port of TidalCycles, utilizing the Web Audio API to schedule precise rhythmic patterns and synthesize audio directly in your browser.</p>
      
      <h4>DAW Controls Reference</h4>
      <div class="reference-grid">
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">▶ PLAY</span>
          <p>Evaluates the code and schedules audio. Crossfades smoothly if already playing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">■ STOP</span>
          <p>Instantly zeroes volume and stops the rhythm scheduler.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">BPM</span>
          <p>Adjusts global Tempo. 1 cycle = 4 Beats.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">LOOP (∞/1)</span>
          <p>Set to infinite or 1 cycle perfectly trimmed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">↑ LOAD</span>
          <p>Load a .strudel or .txt file into the editor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">↓ SAVE</span>
          <p>Download the current editor content as a .strudel file.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">● REC</span>
          <p>Capture an MP4/WebM of the master audio and oscilloscope.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-item">
          <span class="ref-name">⚙ SETTINGS</span>
          <p>Adjust editor font size and view general controls.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button id="btn-info-close" class="modal-cancel">CLOSE</button>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 2000;
  }
  .modal-overlay[hidden] {
    display: none !important;
  }
  .modal-box.info-box {
    background: var(--c-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 30px;
    width: 600px;
    max-width: 90vw;
    max-height: 85vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }
  .modal-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--c-text);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .info-content {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-right: 10px;
    font-family: var(--f-ui);
    scrollbar-width: thin;
    scrollbar-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) transparent;
  }
  .info-content::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 4px;
  }
  .info-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .info-content p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h4 {
    color: var(--c-accent);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .reference-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .ref-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .ref-name {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .ref-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .modal-cancel {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--c-panel2);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .modal-cancel:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--c-text);
  }
</style>
